reviews.text: It's famous for dessert like ice cream with party fruit, simi, or grass jelly.

Good place for dessert! Bring your friends after lunch or dinner. The place is quite big. We were 11 people after dinner and they quickly find us seats. A lot of choices so you will find the one you like from Durian, Mango, Chocolate cake, asian desserts, crème brûlée, banana split and so on... They also close very late.
Great shop with wonderful desserts for a very cheap price! Keep it up!
One in the best dessert in Shum Shui Po district
